  "bib_entries": {
    "124776778": {
      "title": "A W-modification of Godunov's method and its application to two-dimensional non-stationary flows of a dusty gas",
      "abstract": "A new, more accurate, modification of Godunov's method for two-dimensional conservation laws is proposed. Monotonicity of the scheme in the scalar linear case is proved. The scheme is generalized to the flow of two-phase media in the Euler formulation. Results of a numerical experiment on the interaction of a shock wave with a dust cloud are presented."
    }
